{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<ol>\n<li>\n<p>登陆服务器</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ssh 用户名@服务器外网地址</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ssh\">\n      <pre class=\"language-ssh\"><code class=\"language-ssh\">$ ssh root@120.25.197.246</code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>添加新的用户</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>添加新的用户</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ssh\">\n      <pre class=\"language-ssh\"><code class=\"language-ssh\">$ adduser ysbpysbp</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<ul>\n<li>设置密码</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ssh\">\n      <pre class=\"language-ssh\"><code class=\"language-ssh\">$ passwd ysbpysbp</code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>用户组 wheel 拥有 root权限</p>\n<ul>\n<li>把用户放入这个用户组</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ssh\">\n      <pre class=\"language-ssh\"><code class=\"language-ssh\">$ gpasswd -a ysbpysbp wheel </code></pre>\n      </div>\n<ul>\n<li>切换用户</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ssh\">\n      <pre class=\"language-ssh\"><code class=\"language-ssh\">$ u ysbpysbp</code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>同步服务器文件</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"scp\">\n      <pre class=\"language-scp\"><code class=\"language-scp\">sudo scp -p22 -r root@120.25.197.246:/ /Users/zhiyong/server/</code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"参考链接\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>参考链接</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.zhimengzhe.com/mac/104755.html\">scp：Mac使用方法（文件上传与下载服务器）</a></p>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"登陆服务器 ssh 用户名@服务器外网地址 添加新的用户 添加新的用户 设置密码 用户组 wheel 拥有 root权限 把用户放入这个用户组 切换用户 同步服务器文件 参考链接 scp：Mac使用方法（文件上传与下载服务器）","frontmatter":{"title":"ssh管理服务器","cover":null,"date":"2017-09-02T10:08:29.000Z","category":"ssh","tags":["ssh"]},"fields":{"nextTitle":"git workflow","nextSlug":"/tools/git/git-flow/","prevTitle":"node实现页面缓存的策略","prevSlug":"/node/cache/cache/","slug":"/node/server/ssh/","date":"2017-09-01T16:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/node/server/ssh/"}}